href="jonmsterling.xml"
type="local"
addr="jonmsterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A dcpo <fr:tex>A</fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-001S.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-001S">pointed</fr:link> if and only if it is closed under suprema of semidirected subsets.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
